title: CMU Neural Nets for NLP 2017 (19): Document Level Models
description:
This lecture (by Zhengzhong Liu) for CMU CS 11-747, Neural Networks for NLP (Fall 2017) covers:

* Models of Coreference
* Discourse Parsing
* Document Level Prediction

Slides: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/assets/slides/nn4nlp-19-document.pdf

Previous Video: https://youtu.be/EKvkrv4K0qo
Next Video: https://youtu.be/P58GOj91nnA

See more details of the class here: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/
